snippet.title: Vampire: The Masquerade - Lasombra Trailer
snippet.description:
Vampire: The Masquerade - Bloodlines 2 will be released on October 21, 2025. 

The action-RPG video game is the sequel to the cult classic Vampire: The Masquerade - Bloodlines. Vampire: the Masquerade - Bloodlines 2 lets players step into its story through two distinct, alternating perspectives: Elder vampire Phyre and Malkavian detective Fabien.

Today, we bring you a new glimpse into The Night Clan. Meet the Lasombra trainer of Seattle and see Phyre's shadows in action. 

Lasombra starts with "Oblivion" and "Dominate" as clan affinities, and "Shadow Cloak: Feeding on enemies casts you into the shadow, making you harder to see for a period." as the passive ability. Then, as the game progresses, you'll be able to unlock the following Lasombra disciplines: 

"Arms of Ahriman": Trap the opponent's in a straight line with your shadow.
"Shadow Step": Step into your shadow and emerge from the shadow of your target.
"Glimpse of Oblivion": Cause an individual to become afraid, fleeing from their allies.
"Enter Oblivion": Enter a dimension where only you and those touched by your shadow exist.
"Stygian Shroud" - Clan Perk: Prevents mortals from attacking you while feeding.
